    Replacing it with equivalent gray without alpha channel to ensure consistent appearance across devices.-->
    <color name="glia_dark_gray_color">#232323</color>
    <color name="glia_primary_color">#0F6BFF</color>
    <color name="glia_dark_color">#2C0735</color>
